@startuml
actor Usuario
participant "Doctor" as Doctor
participant "Workspace Module" as WS
participant "Profiles Module" as Profiles
participant "Modules Module" as Modules
participant "Relatorios" as Reports

Usuario -> Doctor: run-doctor()
Doctor -> WS: workspace-status()
WS --> Doctor: integridade + permissoes
Doctor -> Profiles: apply-profile()
Profiles --> Doctor: profile modules
Doctor -> Modules: load-modules()
Modules --> Doctor: essenciais/opcionais
Doctor -> Reports: write report and log
Reports --> Doctor: paths
Doctor --> Usuario: texto com falhas, avisos e proximos passos
@enduml
